  "aboutLead": "Chill Factory is a documentary production company\nbuilt on character-driven storytelling.",
  "aboutBody": "We make films that have screened at 100+ festivals, gone viral, and earned hundreds of millions of views online. Founded by Christopher Stoudt — a New Orleans native based in Los Angeles — Chill Factory specializes in finding heart and humor in the most unlikely places.\n\nOur work spans feature docs, shorts, and branded series, told with warmth, patience, and a clear eye. We've partnered with world-class brands and platforms to tell stories that actually mean something to the people watching them.",
